useradd - command for add user

SYNTAX => sudo useradd user_name -m -s /usr/bin/bash -g users -c "comment"
          sudo passwd user-name

-m      => for defalut home
-s      => for default shell
-g      => for default group
-c      => for comment
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
userdel - command for delete the user

sudo userdel user_name        -> for remove the user but it can't be remove user from home  
sudo userdel -r user-name     -> for remove user completely 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
